Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.73,0:02:56.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:174737,176439}All right, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.17,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:178966,181177}We still have a lot of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.17,0:03:03.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:181177,183179}Hmm, actually…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.17,0:03:07.18,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:183179,187183}Miki, Mr. Egawa\Nis just pleased with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.76,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:187183,189769}That's why he let you off\Nearlier than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:12.18,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:189769,192188}No, I never said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.18,0:03:15.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:192188,195233}It's because the song isn't yet finished.\NI need to make a few corrections.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.40,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:195233,196401}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.81,0:03:18.94,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:197819,198945}Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:198945,200988}I'm the one who's\Nresponsible for my success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:25.28,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:200988,205284}Mr. Egawa's melody, Mr. Nohara's lyrics.\NUchida Productions, Orion Records.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.28,0:03:26.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:205284,206828}Everything is first class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:31.41,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:207703,211416}But none of this matters\Nif I don't give my absolute best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:34.87,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:211416,214877}That's why I have to take\Nmy lessons very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.83,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:214877,216838}That's well put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.96,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:217338,219966}I'll be working on your song all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.75,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:219966,221759}It'll get even tougher\Nfrom tomorrow on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.34,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:221759,223344}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:49.93,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:225721,229934}I wonder how long he's going to keep\Nyou waiting like this, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:229934,232854}I don't mind it.\NI've grown used to it, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:58.48,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:233521,238484}Maybe it's a part of something deeper and\Nhe has a plan for you that we don't see…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.61,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:239402,241612}That'd be terrific.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:06.53,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:245074,246534}I've brought you some snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:08.41,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:246534,248411}We don't need them.\NDon't interrupt us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:248411,249245}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.58,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:253583,254584}Shimamaru Mk II{NOTE:㐧2 志摩丸}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.12,0:04:15.54,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:252123,255543}That's Shimamaru Mk II.\NTake a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:18.00,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:255543,258004}It's used by pearl divers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:20.67,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:258004,260673}The ship has a tonnage of 1500 tons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.67,0:04:26.01,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:260673,266012}Using this aft passenger area,\Nwe'll arrange a party for around 300 people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:268764,269974}It's gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.93,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:269974,272935}You'll have a beautiful view of\NShima Peninsula from the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.81,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:272935,274812}The slides don't do the justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.35,0:04:36.81,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:275354,276814}{\i1}Pearl divers…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.65,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:277190,281652}There is no way that a debut party\Nin such conditions turns out to be a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.44,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:281652,283446}But let's hear opinion of your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.44,0:04:45.28,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:283446,285281}It exceeds my wildest expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.28,0:04:47.65,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:285281,287658}I'm very satisfied, to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.82,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:287658,291829}It's nice to hear your praise, especially\Nthat it was my idea for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:56.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:293706,296167}How does the schedule look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:57.91,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:296167,297919}Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:02.17,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:297919,302173}We'll open the party\Nnext week, on August 5th.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:05.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:302173,305176}Next week…\NThat's rather quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:305176,308054}I just finished the song last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:11.80,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:308054,311807}Oh, Mr. Egawa, your strict\Nguidance is unparalleled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:13.60,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:311807,313601}There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.60,0:05:16.14,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:313601,316145}I just have to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.31,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:316145,317313}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.65,0:05:27.03,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:322652,327031}In that case, I would like us to go\Nto Shima Peninsula as early as tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.03,0:05:28.57,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:327031,328574}and begin practicing already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:30.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:328574,330201}We'll practice by the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:330826,331702}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:36.66,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:333704,336666}It sounds really good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:39.21,Default,President,0,0,0,,{TIME:336666,339210}I could even rent a hotel room\Nfor you two to make things easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:40.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:339710,340711}Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.58,0:05:45.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:342588,345633}{\i1}He's fully dedicated to my debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:345633,348469}{\i1}Nozomi will become a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:50.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:348928,350179}See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.43,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:350179,352431}Thank you for everything, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:05:59.14,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:357478,359146}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:00.02,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:359146,360022}Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:03.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:361232,363859}Sir, there was a call for you\Nfrom Nohara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:05.73,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:363859,365736}Thanks, I'll call him back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:08.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:365736,368823}By the way, do you think\Nyou could take a trip for a week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:368823,370032}A trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.70,0:06:14.49,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:370700,374495}We decided to hold Kōda-kun's\Ndebut party in Shima Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:374495,375288}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:19.08,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:375288,379083}We're going there tomorrow.\NI'll teach her in the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:21.04,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:379083,381043}Will you come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:22.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:381961,382837}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.15,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:407612,409155}Take care of the baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:49.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:409155,409989}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:416871,418289}Sir, could you open the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.08,Default,Driver,0,0,0,,{TIME:418289,420082}I'll take care of your baggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.54,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:420541,422543}Actually, it's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:06.13,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:424211,426130}Yes, of course, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:09.84,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:427006,429842}Why did he insist\Nto take Nozomi with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:12.59,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:430551,432595}She's your assistant, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:14.22,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:432595,434221}She has her uses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:15.72,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:434221,435723}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:18.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:435723,438851}But I don't like how he brought her\Nwithout my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.39,0:07:23.60,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:439393,443606}Keep her close and make her work hard.\NI can't always stay with you, it'd look bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:26.35,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:443606,446359}I have my lessons.\NOf course I won't let her fool around.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.40,0:07:32.49,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:449403,452490}This room has the best view\Nin the entire hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:34.07,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:452490,454075}Hurry up, Nozomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:34.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:454075,454575}Right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:44.54,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:461457,464543}Nozomi, let's take a walk\Nwhen things calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.25,0:07:45.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:465252,465920}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.62,0:07:48.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:466629,468297}{\i1}A walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:50.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:468297,470633}{\i1}I thought we didn't\Nhave time for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:486565,487525}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:08.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:487525,488442}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.86,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:488442,490861}I want you to become a diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:12.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:490861,492488}A diver?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.48,0:08:13.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:492488,493447}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:500079,502456}You mean, like those\Npeople over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.45,0:08:24.45,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:502456,504458}Yes, just like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.89,0:08:49.10,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:524895,529108}You'd be bored to stay in the hotel\Nwith nothing to do all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:529108,532528}Instead, you could bring us\Na basket of tasty abalone every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:53.94,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:532528,533946}Think you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.94,0:08:56.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:533946,536031}Yes… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.03,0:08:58.45,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:536031,538451}With all I have to do,\NI can't go around fishing for abalone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:09:01.20,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:538451,541203}What do you say?\NDo we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:541203,542329}Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:05.70,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:542329,545708}Good girl.\NI'll talk to the divers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:14.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:552590,554884}{\i1}Is this why he brought me here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.88,0:09:16.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:554884,556886}{\i1}To collect shellfish for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:31.35,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:570232,571358}Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.15,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:572943,575154}Oh, you must be the girl\Nfrom yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.40,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:576405,577406}That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:38.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:577406,578574}Let's work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.86,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:578574,580868}Finally, a pretty girl joined in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.66,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:580868,583662}Wouldn't you be better off\Ntaking a stroll or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.83,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:583662,586832}She has small butt,\Nso she won't sink easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:51.67,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:589168,591670}Alright, let's get to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.92,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:591670,593923}I'm their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.71,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:593923,595716}Stay close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:596675,597760}Yes ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.52,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:606101,608521}Don't just stand there. Jump in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.52,0:10:11.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:608521,611023}Right. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:627122,629083}No one's surfaced yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:32.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:630251,632169}Alright, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:41.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:634797,641679}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It slowly decays in my mind  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:胸にしまうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:641679,644807}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Ahh  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ああ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:47.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:646308,647726}No! You're butchering it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.06,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:649228,651063}Listen, it's all about control!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.43,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:651063,652439}Raise your voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:53.89,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:652439,653899}"Ahh", "ahh", "ahh"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.90,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:653899,655901}Pay attention to the notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:56.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:655901,656735}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:58.27,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:656735,658279}Let's try the intro again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:06.03,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:658821,666036}{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Ahh, where have you gone?  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ああ、あなたはいない}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.71,0:11:15.50,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:673711,675504}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.50,0:11:18.29,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:675504,678299}You've just started.\NDon't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:26.30,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:684346,686307}You got two, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.84,0:11:28.85,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:686849,688851}Oh, why the long face?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:31.85,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:688851,691854}It's pretty good for a first-timer.\NYou'll get better eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:33.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:691854,693063}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.06,0:11:35.64,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:693063,695649}Actually, I made a bet\Nthat you won't get a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.65,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:695649,697651}One more and you can cook a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.73,0:11:43.53,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:699737,703532}If you keep at it,\Nyou can become a pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:46.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:703532,706869}Do you really think so?\NI don't think I have enough lung capacity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.86,0:11:50.99,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:706869,710998}No, sweetie. The longer you stay under,\Nthe longer you'll be able to hold your breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:51.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:710998,711707}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:54.58,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:711707,714585}If you don't believe me,\Nsee for yourself next time we dive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.25,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:716128,717254}Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:58.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:717254,718339}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:01.09,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:719590,721091}How was your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:01.84,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:721091,721842}Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:10.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:728140,730809}Oh, it's just two…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.80,0:12:12.14,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:730809,732144}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.52,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:732144,734521}That won't cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:20.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:739985,740945}But, sir!
Comment: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:30.12,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:750120,750120}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:753582,756126}Even two were just fine.\NI did great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.33,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:756126,758337}How could you just\Nthrow them back to sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:39.63,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:758337,759630}Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:43.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:759630,763425}You should not use expressions\Nsuch as "I did great" so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:47.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:763425,767137}If you had really done great, you should've\Ncollected more than the other divers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.59,0:12:52.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:769598,772226}But I just started today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:56.14,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:772226,776146}That's my whole point. If you engage them\Nthinking like a beginner, you'll never succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.94,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:776146,779942}Those women endured rigorous training,\None that you and I can't probably even fathom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.19,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:779942,783195}"Doing great" means you should\Nput forth at least as much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:05.61,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:783195,785614}I told you to become a diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.11,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:785614,787116}I meant a professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.11,0:13:09.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:787116,789201}That's ridiculous. I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:12.12,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:789201,792121}If you don't understand\Nwhat I want to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:14.45,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:792121,794456}go back to Tōkyō at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:16.20,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:794456,796208}Ah… Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:19.42,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:796208,799420}If you have nothing more to say,\Nfocus on collecting more clams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.08,0:13:24.17,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:801088,804174}Kōda-kun is clenching her teeth\Nand studying like never before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:31.76,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:807886,811765}{\i1}Why on earth does\Nhe want me to become a diver?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.43,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:813767,815436}Don't be so discouraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.47,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:815436,817479}You won't live long\Nif you worry too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:38.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:817479,818272}I…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:41.48,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:818272,821483}You'll forget everything in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:43.48,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:821483,823485}One more round, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.27,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:823485,825279}'Aight, break's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.27,0:13:47.28,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:825279,827281}Let's get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.57,0:13:53.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:828574,833454}I don't understand\NMr. Egawa anymore at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:54.62,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:833454,834621}Why is he doing all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.34,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:849553,852347}{\i1}I had two goals\Nin coming to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:16.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:852347,856643}{\i1}The first one was to train\NKōda Miki for her debut. The other one…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.64,0:14:22.60,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:856643,862608}Well, I can't help but wonder how she'd react\Nif she learned that I absolutely hate abalone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:28.48,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:864151,868489}{\i1}Nozomi kept diving and every day\Nshe picked up more and more shellfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:32.20,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:868489,872201}{\i1}She was gradually\Nretaking her confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.83,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:876872,878832}Today was my best day yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.83,0:14:39.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:878832,879708}Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.70,0:14:40.54,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:879708,880542}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:42.37,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:880542,882377}Wow, I like what I'm seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:47.04,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:882377,887049}I've got to say, mister,\NNozomi-chan's spirit impressed me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:49.34,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:887049,889343}She has the potential\Nto become a mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:889343,890302}Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.80,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:890302,891804}A mermaid?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:54.18,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:891804,894181}It's a master diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.18,0:14:57.72,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:894181,897726}Do you think you could\Ntrain her to become one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:14:59.18,Default,Diver,0,0,0,,{TIME:897726,899186}Oh, with pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:00.85,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:899186,900854}Now you're just teasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.64,0:15:07.15,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:903649,907152}All right, then. How about\Nwe eat one of these tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.32,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:907152,909321}Tomorrow is Kōda's debut party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:10.11,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:909321,910114}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:13.65,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:910114,913659}The cruise ship is getting decorated.\NThere's a lot of commotion around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:18.58,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:913659,918580}It will be a big day.\NYes, a very big day for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.75,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:919623,921750}I hope for a full basket\Ntomorrow as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:22.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:921750,922751}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:24.00,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:922751,924002}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:28.13,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:924002,928132}Do not forget that you too will become\Na great singer. Make sure not to catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:30.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:929258,930884}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.88,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:931635,933887}It's all part of your preparation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:41.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:938725,941478}So it's part of preparing me\Nto become a singer…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:44.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:941478,944398}But is it really?\NHow is this supposed to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.40,0:15:54.19,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:952406,954199}You look fantastic, Miki.\NIt fits you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:56.16,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:954199,956160}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:16:00.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:956160,960289}It's very nice.\NIt's so gorgeous and dazzling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:02.20,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:960289,962207}You've become good at flattery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:962207,963333}And the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:04.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:963333,964251}Looks good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:06.62,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:964251,966628}I heard that you became a diver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:07.29,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:966628,967296}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:08.54,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:967296,968547}Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:09.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:968547,969631}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:13.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:969631,973510}Evidently, you've realized you can't succeed\Nas a singer and found something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.51,0:16:18.01,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:974511,978015}I, on the other hand, can't picture\Nmyself doing anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:24.89,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:982477,984897}I'd better get going.\NIt's time for my last lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.53,0:16:36.78,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:994531,996783}Will I be fine, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:39.28,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:997743,999286}So even you can get nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:41.28,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:999286,1001288}I guess it's natural.\NDon't worry, it will go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.91,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003498,1005918}The guests are beginning to arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:52.67,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009922,1012674}How about one last\Ninspection of your stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:54.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012674,1014676}Sure. I'll go at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:02.55,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019431,1022559}I can already see how presumptuous\Nshe becomes in a few weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:25.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041662,1045707}I caught so many,\Nno wonder I'm so exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.70,0:17:27.70,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045707,1047709}Look at you, you cutie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:41.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1059513,1061974}Mom, where is my score?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:43.68,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061974,1063684}The score?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:46.14,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1063684,1066144}It was on the table at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:48.77,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066144,1068772}What? It wasn't in the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.60,0:17:51.81,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1069606,1071817}I thought you took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:53.81,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071817,1073819}So it's still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:55.19,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073819,1075195}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.73,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075195,1077739}I can't sing without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.24,0:18:00.70,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078240,1080701}But you remember the lyrics, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:07.54,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080701,1087541}No, Mr. Egawa left me lots of important notes\Non the score that tell me exactly how to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:10.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087541,1090752}It took me a week to learn it,\Nand that's with the notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.33,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1090752,1093338}I understand.\NSo it's just indispensable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093338,1095257}I can't sing without the score.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:18.42,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095257,1098427}We still have some time.\NLet's get someone to bring it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:18:19.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098427,1099678}No, we can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.67,0:18:21.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099678,1101388}What would people say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.68,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101388,1103682}What kind of musician\Nforgets their score?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:25.05,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103682,1105058}I suppose you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.05,0:18:27.56,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105058,1107561}We have to get it in a way\Nthat won't get noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:29.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107561,1109479}Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:31.23,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109479,1111231}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.73,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112065,1114735}There are a lot of people\Nwho know how to swim in these parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:40.78,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116111,1120782}There would be nothing strange\Nif someone boarded the ship to rest for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:41.74,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120782,1121742}I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:46.99,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125704,1126997}Mine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.16,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126997,1128165}Mine-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:51.00,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129708,1131001}This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:57.75,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132377,1137758}We got a call from Kōda-san. She's asked\Nyou to carry this envelope to the ship at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:59.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1137758,1139092}She's asked for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:02.34,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139092,1142346}You must swim up to the ship and deliver it\Nwithout getting noticed by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:03.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142346,1143638}Wait, what? Swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:06.05,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143638,1146058}Yes. The score is protected\Nby three plastic casings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.26,0:19:08.56,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147267,1148560}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:16.73,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154232,1156735}You're tired. Are you sure\Nyou can make it within half an hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:18.82,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156735,1158820}I'll be fine.\NIt's just about 2 kilometers, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:19.57,Default,Hotel staff,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158820,1159571}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:23.57,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162366,1163575}{\i1}Good, the waves are small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.12,0:19:31.58,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170123,1171583}She's late…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:34.00,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172209,1174002}How are the preparations going?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.00,0:19:36.75,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174002,1176755}We're almost finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.75,0:19:39.84,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176755,1179841}We're starting in 30 minutes.\NSee you on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:42.34,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180425,1182344}Where is she?\NWhat is she doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:19:58.86,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197526,1198860}Miki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.53,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201196,1202531}What is she doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:05.11,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202531,1205117}She's been diving for a week.\NShe's slow as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:10.12,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209204,1210122}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1217921,1219131}Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:21.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219798,1221633}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223427,1225220}Alright, now please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225220,1226513}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:27.84,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226513,1227848}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:28.22,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227848,1228223}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.93,0:20:33.93,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1230934,1233937}You're trying to sabotage\Nmy debut, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.60,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233937,1235605}Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:38.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1235605,1238442}There's a hole in the package.\NAnyone would've noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:40.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238442,1240068}Why didn't you check it before?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240068,1242446}I did! But it must've\Nbeen too small to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1242446,1243613}I won't forgive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:45.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243613,1245615}You ruined my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:48.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246950,1248618}You're a terrible person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.61,0:20:51.45,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248618,1251455}Why did you do this to me? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:55.75,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252873,1255750}Don't even try to apologize.\NNothing can be done now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.75,0:20:57.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255750,1257127}Calm down, Miki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.00,0:21:01.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259004,1261590}I'll replace your score.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.63,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261590,1262632}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:07.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1264217,1267137}I listened to your lessons and\Nlearned your song for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.89,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268054,1269890}I'll sing it for you\Nand you'll remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.39,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269890,1271391}B-But…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.47,0:21:14.64,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1272476,1274644}We don't have time for games.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:20.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276938,1280025}You care about your debut, right?\NIt's sink or swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:32.32,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290702,1292329}We'll do it one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.41,0:21:37.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293413,1297250}T-That'd be terrific.\NI'll join in when it comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.84,0:21:49.63,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305842,1309638}{\i1}Look at her. I didn't even teach her,\Nand she's completely mastered the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.63,0:21:52.64,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309638,1312641}{\i1}And looks like training\Nwith the divers didn't go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.64,0:21:55.93,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312641,1315936}{\i1}Her breath is deeper,\Nand makes the song resonate better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:43.34,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300003,1303340}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm dead  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:48.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303340,1308470}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm dead on the inside  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.47,0:21:52.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1308470,1312182}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It's beyond words  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:傷ついた}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.18,0:21:57.81,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1312182,1317812}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  My wings are broken  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:羽を労る}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:22:02.31,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1317812,1322317}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm like a wounded bird  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:小鳩のように}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:06.86,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322317,1326863}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思い出を}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:15.66,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326863,1335664}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  burns hot in my heart  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ずっと胸にしまうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:25.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335664,1345215}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Ahh, where have you gone?  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ああ、あなたはいない}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.05,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1354641,1356059}{\i1}Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:37.60,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356059,1357602}{\i1}Mine Nozomi, the diver!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.60,0:22:40.23,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:1357602,1360230}{\i1}I have but one thing to say.\NYou are one amazing girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:32.05,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348969,1352055}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm dead  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃えて}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:36.85,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1352055,1356851}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm dead on the inside  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:燃え尽きた今}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.85,0:22:40.23,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1356851,1360230}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It's beyond words  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:傷ついた}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:45.44,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1360230,1365443}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  My wings are broken  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:羽を労る}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:49.61,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1365443,1369614}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  I'm like a wounded bird  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:小鳩のように}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.61,0:22:53.82,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1369614,1373827}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思い出を}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:23:02.21,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1373827,1382210}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  burns hot in my heart  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ずっと胸にしまうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.21,0:23:10.46,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1382210,1390468}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Ahh, where have you gone?  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:ああ、あなたはいない}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.46,0:23:17.97,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1390468,1397976}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  comes back to haunt me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思いでをやさしく}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.97,0:23:22.98,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:1397976,1402981}{\fad(0,2000)\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It slowly decays in my mind  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:胸に}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.71,0:23:12.30,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1389718,1392304}{\i1}Looks like the debut is a success.
Comment: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:28.09,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1408094,1408094}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.76,0:23:34.30,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1408762,1414309}{\i1}After returning to Tōkyō, Nozomi is overjoyed\Nto finally have the chance to sing in front of Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:39.94,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1414309,1419940}{\i1}However, Egawa, upon hearing Nozomi sing,\Ntells her to sing in a club in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.94,0:23:44.44,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1419940,1424444}{\i1}That club turns out to be an uncanny\Ngathering place for local black people.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:47.15,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1424444,1427155}{\i1}Nozomi is terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:52.61,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1427155,1432619}{\i1}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"The Song Of The Port".
